 · 剛才不久













                  發問者的評分
                















 1. There are different since 人體生理學 is sort of subcategories of 生理學(physiology):the branch of science that describes mechanisms and functions in organisms.There are 10 subcategories shown below (more may be shown on subsequent pages). AAnimal physiologyEElectrophysiology Exercise physiologyFFungal physiologyIImmunologyMMetabolismNNeurophysiologyOOrgan systemsPPhysiologists2. As for 解剖生理學, it is combination of "physiology" and "anatomy".Contents: 
圖片參考：http://distance.stcc.edu/AandP/_themes/cactus/cacbul1a.gif 
Unit 28:  Fetal DevelopmentHope it helps. Let me know if further questions. 

